      to Jonathan Davies

  [ Barry Warsaw ]
  * In Python 2.7, locale.format() input test has gotten more strict.  It
    does not allow trailing text after the format string.  Change this to
    locale.format_string().  See Python issue 10379.  (LP: #673297)

